323
00:26:14,980 --> 00:26:16,560
Okay.

324
00:26:18,680 --> 00:26:21,960
anong ginagawa mo Naghahanap ka ba ng isang partikular na libro?

325
00:26:21,960 --> 00:26:24,400
Hindi, hindi iyon.

