348
00:27:37,490 --> 00:27:41,500
Oh, kaya pala laging malinis ang bahay niya.

349
00:27:41,500 --> 00:27:44,100
No wonder.

350
00:27:44,100 --> 00:27:49,430
Ano ang mga selula ni Wung? I bet it so different from our Housework cell.

351
