Pero.. tignan mo si Wung. Tingnan kung gaano siya kaiba.

401
00:31:19,620 --> 00:31:23,150
Wung, kape.

402
00:31:23,150 --> 00:31:27,780
♫ Kahit alam kong wala akong magagawa sa puso ko ♫

403
00:31:31,650 --> 00:31:33,950
